<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Submit Grievance | Union Support</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #003366;
      --accent: #66aaff;
      --danger: #be123c;
      --bg: #fdfdfe;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --text: #334155;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --radius: 12px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f1f5f9;
      color: var(--text);
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #1e293b);
      color: white;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    header p {
      opacity: 0.8;
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: -40px auto 60px;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    /* --- Form Card --- */
    .form-card {
      background: var(--white);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 40px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .confidential-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      background: #fff1f2;
      color: var(--danger);
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 99px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #fecdd3;
    }

    .form-section-title {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .form-section-title::after {
      content: "";
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      flex: 1;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #475569;
    }

    .input-icon-wrapper {
      position: relative;
    }

    .input-icon-wrapper i {
      position: absolute;
      left: 14px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #94a3b8;
    }

    input, select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 12px 12px 42px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      background: #f8fafc;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    textarea {
      padding: 12px;
      height: 150px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    input:focus, textarea:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent);
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(102, 170, 255, 0.1);
    }

    /* --- Submit Button --- */
    .btn-submit {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--danger);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-submit:hover {
      background: #9f1239;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(190, 18, 60, 0.2);
    }

    .help-text {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .form-card { padding: 25px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Formal Grievance Submission</h1>
  <p>Your rights are protected. Your voice will be heard.</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <div class="form-card">
    <div class="confidential-tag">
      <i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i> Strictly Confidential
    </div>

    <form>
      <div class="form-section-title">Complainant Information</div>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Full Name</label>
          <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
            <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
            <input type="text" placeholder="John Doe" required>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Department</label>
          <div class="input-icon-wrapper">
            <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
            <input type="text" placeholder="e.g. Operations" required>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-section-title">Incident Details</div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Nature of Grievance</label>
        <textarea placeholder="Please provide a detailed description of the incident, including dates, times, and any witnesses..."></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">
        Submit Formal Grievance <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
      </button>

      <div class="help-text">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Once submitted, a Union Steward will contact you within 24-48 hours.
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
